FBIS3-55373 "drsov005_v_94009" FBIS-SOV-94-005 Document Type:Daily Report 7 Jan 1994 Lithuania Officials Receive Pensions, Wages Increase LD0601163694 Vilnius Radio Vilnius Network in Lithuanian 1400 GMT 6 Jan 93 LD0601163694 Vilnius Radio Vilnius Network Language: Lithuanian Article Type:BFN [Text] At today's news conference by the prime minister, journalists were informed that the government has decided to increase pensions and wages of officials at institutions maintained from the budget from 1 January. The prime minister said this will not completely compensate for December's price increases but it is something. According to Adolfas Slezevicius, inflation was 6.2 percent in December.
